”With fondest memories of my dearest son Mark and his dearest wife Frances September 7th 1996

You will Never be Forgotten by all of us who loved you so dearly - AME"¼
®In loving memory of Susan Firman
A devoted mother, grandmother, sister and friend
who loved arts & crafts and drinking tea
We will miss you
29. 10. 1957-08. 10. 2021"▓
»IN LOVING MEMORY OF
LOFTUS HORN 1908-1999
FROM HIS FAMILY AND SPECIAL FRIENDS

Joyce Horn 1913-2006
Beloved Wife of Lof, Mother of Fay
And Wendy, Grandmother of Danielle"╗
ĖSimon John Kwiecinski
01.09.1973 - 06.10.2013
(Dada, Kwif. Special K, Ski, K-Dog)
Remembering you is easy, we do it every day
It's just the pain of losing you, that never goes away"┐
